q1ss: Affine Partition Hashes
=================================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-green.svg
    :target: https://docs.python.org/3.10/
    :alt: Python versions

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/aphash.svg
